<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <title>Axis and Allies Battle Calculator</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet"
          href="../static/style.css"/>
    <style>
        table, th, td {
  border: 1px solid black;
}
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<p>Monte Carlo calculator for determining the chances of winning an attack in Axis and Allies. Note: does not
care about the relationship between submarines and planes, but might one day.</p>
</body>

<form method="GET" action="{{ request.route_path('aaa_battle_calculator') }}">
